statements: SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance;
SELECT maintenance_type, service_provider, maintenance_date FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance;
SELECT asset_id, maintenance_type, maintenance_date FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance WHERE maintenance_type = 'scheduled';
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance WHERE maintenance_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance WHERE maintenance_type = 'Calibration' ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT asset_id, maintenance_date, maintenance_type FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance WHERE service_provider = 'Quantum Solutions' AND maintenance_date < '2022-01-01'
SELECT technician_id, COUNT(*) AS maintenance_count FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance GROUP BY technician_id ORDER BY maintenance_count DESC
SELECT * FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance WHERE technician_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000' AND maintenance_notes IS NOT NULL
SELECT asset_id, maintenance_type, maintenance_date FROM QuantumHardwareMaintenance WHERE maintenance_type IN ('Calibration', 'Repair') ORDER BY maintenance_date ASC
SELECT * FROM maintenance_history;
SELECT id, maintenance_date, maintenance_type FROM maintenance_history ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT technician_name, maintenance_type, maintenance_date FROM maintenance_history WHERE quantum_hardware_id = 123;
SELECT service_date, service_type, service_description FROM service_history ORDER BY service_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_history WHERE technician_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM maintenance_history WHERE maintenance_type = 'Scheduled Maintenance';
SELECT id, maintenance_type, technician_name FROM maintenance_history ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT id, maintenance_date, technician_name FROM maintenance_history WHERE maintenance_date >= '2021-01-01' AND maintenance_date <= '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM service_history WHERE service_type = 'Repair' ORDER BY service_date ASC;
SELECT service_date, service_type, service_description FROM service_history WHERE service_date > '2021-06-30';
SELECT system_name, maintenance_date FROM quantum_hardware_systems;
SELECT system_name, service_provider FROM quantum_hardware_systems WHERE system_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_logs ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC;
SELECT system_name, service_cost FROM quantum_hardware_systems JOIN service_history ON quantum_hardware_systems.system_id = service_history.system_id;
SELECT service_provider, COUNT(*) AS service_count FROM quantum_hardware_systems GROUP BY service_provider;
SELECT system_name, maintenance_date FROM quantum_hardware_systems WHERE system_id = 1
SELECT * FROM maintenance_logs ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC
SELECT service_provider, COUNT(*) AS total_services FROM quantum_hardware_systems GROUP BY service_provider HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
SELECT sl.system_id, sl.maintenance_type, sh.service_cost FROM maintenance_logs sl JOIN service_history sh ON sl.system_id = sh.system_id WHERE sh.service_cost > 500

SELECT system_name, maintenance_date, technician_name FROM quantum_hardware_systems qhs INNER JOIN maintenance_logs ml ON qhs.system_id = ml.system_id INNER JOIN service_history sh ON qhs.system_id = sh.system_id WHERE ml.maintenance_type = 'Repair' ORDER BY maintenance_date ASC
SELECT * FROM maintenance_log ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT system_id, maintenance_type FROM maintenance_log WHERE maintenance_type = 'Routine Inspection';
SELECT * FROM service_log WHERE service_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT system_id, service_type, service_date FROM service_log ORDER BY service_date ASC;
SELECT team_name, team_lead FROM maintenance_team WHERE team_size > 5;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_log ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT system_id, maintenance_type FROM maintenance_log WHERE maintenance_type='Repair' ORDER BY system_id ASC;
SELECT team_name, team_lead FROM maintenance_team WHERE team_size > 5;
SELECT * FROM service_log WHERE service_date >= '2022-01-01' AND service_type='Inspection';
SELECT name, manufacturer, purchase_date FROM hardware_system ORDER BY name ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_history;
SELECT maintenance_description, maintenance_date FROM maintenance_history WHERE maintenance_id = 1;
SELECT hardware_name, manufacturer, model FROM hardware_systems WHERE hardware_id = 3;
SELECT technician_name, technician_specialization FROM technicians WHERE technician_id = 2;
SELECT maintenance_id, technician_id FROM maintenance_technicians ORDER BY maintenance_id ASC, technician_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM maintenance_history ORDER BY maintenance_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT maintenance_id, maintenance_description, maintenance_date FROM maintenance_history WHERE hardware_id = 12345;
SELECT service_description, service_date, hardware_name FROM service_history JOIN hardware_systems ON service_history.hardware_id = hardware_systems.hardware_id;

SELECT maintenance_id, hardware_name, technician_name FROM maintenance_history JOIN maintenance_technicians ON maintenance_history.maintenance_id = maintenance_technicians.maintenance_id JOIN technicians ON maintenance_technicians.technician_id = technicians.technician_id;

SELECT manufacturer, COUNT(*) AS total_maintenance FROM hardware_systems JOIN maintenance_history ON hardware_systems.hardware_id = maintenance_history.hardware_id GROUP BY manufacturer ORDER BY total_maintenance DESC;
